title: Cyrillic domain
extract: The process of installing IDN country code domains began with a long period of testing in a set of subdomains in the test top-level domain. Eleven domains used language-native scripts or alphabets, such as δοκιμή, meaning test in Greek. ... For example, the Cyrillic name of Russia's IDN ccTLD is "рф".
